# Input

```css
@starting-style {
    h1 {
        background-color: transparent;
    }


    @layer          foo {
        @starting-style {
            background-color: transparent;
        }

        div {


            height: 100px;
        }
    }
}

```


# Formatted

```css
@starting-style {
	h1 {
		background-color: transparent;
	}

	@layer foo {
		@starting-style {
			background-color: transparent;
		}

		div {
			height: 100px;
		}
	}
}

```
